2026-0143
2026-02-24GACExport and Import Permits ActOrder Amending the Import Control List (2026-1)Order Amending the Import Control List (2026-1) in order to add a list of electric vehicles originating in China under a new item 195, thus making import permits a requirement for these goods to be lawfully imported into Canada.Registration: SOR/2026-0032 Publication Date: 2026-03-11
subject: Order Amending the Import Control List (2026-1)
precis: Order Amending the Import Control List (2026-1) in order to add a list of electric vehicles originating in China under a new item 195, thus making import permits a requirement for these goods to be lawfully imported into Canada.
